examples.en: Oh, how wonderful!
Wonderful evening, what?
It was a wonderful party.
We had a wonderful time in Spain.
As a writer, he's wonderful.
She came home with wonderful news.
It was just wonderful to see her again.
I love the spring  it's a wonderful time of the year.
You did a wonderful job.
It's wonderful to finally meet you.
The flower has a wonderful scent.
What a wonderful opportunity! I'm so happy for you.
It's wonderful what doctors can do nowadays.
The rooms were filled with wonderful works of art.
This dinner is wonderful! he enthused.
She carried herself with a wonderful air.
It felt wonderful to be wearing clean clothes again.
He's not that wonderful. He's bad-tempered for one thing.
I happened upon the most wonderful bakery not very far from here.
At the time I thought he was wonderful, but I'm older and wiser now.
He can write wonderful anacreontics.
Venice is a wonderful city to explore.
The dishwasher is a wonderful invention.
The city is wonderful seen from the air.
Her essay was a wonderful piece of writing.
It was wonderful to visit our national parks.
He has a wonderful whimsical sense of humour.
The house has wonderful views over the valley.
It was wonderful that we could see each other.
The wonderful desserts are made on the premises.
